* Output to I/O buffer ptr in (U), updates I.IOCT
SPCSTR bsr OUTSPC Output a space

* Output string (X), followed by space
STRSPC bsr CPYSTR Output the string

* Output space (only if previous char was not)
OUTSPC pshs D,U Save regs
 bsr DCLF check for right MARGIN
 bcc OUTSP9 ..Yes; return
 ldu I.IOPT Get the buf ptr
 lda #V$SPAC
 cmpa -1,U Was prev char a space?
 beq OUTSP9 Exit if so
 cmpu I.IOBG Beginning of buffer?
 bne PUTCH2 ..no; print space
OUTSP9 puls D,U,PC Exit

