* Put Char (A) in Output Buffer

PUTCR lda #V$CR put EOL in buffer
PUTCHR pshs D,U
 ldu I.IOPT
PUTCH2 sta ,U+
 ldd I.IOPT
 subd I.IOBG
 tsta
 bne PUTCH9
 inc I.IOCT
 stu I.IOPT
PUTCH9 puls D,U,PC

