 ldd P.PGMB,X Get I-Code area offset
 addd I.APRC
 std I.ICBG
 ldd P.DSCB,X
 addd I.APRC Compute i-code limit
 std I.ICLM Set I-Code area end (+1)
 std I.STBG
 ldd P.SIZE,X
 subd P.DSCB,X Compute symbol tbl size + desc tbl size
